<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="..\config8\suzuki.xsl" ?><!DOCTYPE suzuki [<!ENTITY % sdatacharaents SYSTEM "..\config8\sdatacharaents.txt">%sdatacharaents;]><suzuki><manual>
<section sectnbr = "5B">
<servcat sctnbr = "05" scnbr = "02">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENCP70A5206027" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "02" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Differential Disassembly and Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENCP70A5206011">Manual Transaxle Unit Dismounting and Remounting</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENCP70A5206016">Manual Transaxle Assembly Disassembly and Reassembly</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENCP70A5206026">Differential Components</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A5206027001">
<title>
Disassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using special tools and hydraulic press, remove right bearing (1).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B029">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09924-74510">
09924–74510
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B030">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09924-74590">
09924–74590
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I4RS0B521049.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "48.061mm" ver = "01" gw = "182" gh = "120"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove left bearing in the same manner as Step 1).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Support differential case with soft jawed vise and remove final gear bolts then remove final gear.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using special tool and hammer, remove differential pinion shaft pin (1) and then disassemble component parts.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B031">
<s-part>
(C)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09922-85811">
09922–85811
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I4RS0B521051.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.975mm" ver = "01" gw = "119" gh = "131"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A5206027002">
<title>
Reassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Assemble differential gear and measure thrust play of differential gear as follows.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B032">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09900-20607">
09900–20607
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B033">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09900-20701">
09900–20701
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<spec>
<title>
Differential gear thrust play
</title>
<ptxt>
0.03 – 0.31 mm (0.001 – 0.012 in.)
</ptxt>
</spec>
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
Left side [A]
</emph>
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Hold differential assembly with soft jawed vise and apply measuring tip of dial gauge to top surface of gear (2).
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Using 2 screwdrivers (1), move gear up and down and read movement of dial gauge pointer.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
Right side [B]
</emph>
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Using similar procedure to the left side, set dial gauge tip to gear (2) shoulder.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Move gear up and down by hand and read dial gauge.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I3RH0A520083.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "103.240mm" ver = "01" gw = "176" gh = "276"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
If thrust play is out of specification, select suitable thrust washer from the available size, install it and check again that specified thrust play is obtained.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Hold differential assembly with soft jawed vise (3), install final gear (2) as shown in figure and then tighten new bolts (1) to specified torque.
</ptxt>
<torque>
<torqueitem id = "T5B023">
<t-part>
Final gear bolt
</t-part>
<t-part1>
a
</t-part1>
<t-value1>
90
</t-value1>
<t-value2>
9.2
</t-value2>
<t-value3>
66.5
</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I4RS0B521052.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "85.333mm" ver = "01" gw = "173" gh = "225"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using special tool and hammer, install new differential pinion shaft pin (1) till the depth from differential case (2) surface is about 1 mm (0.04 in.).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B034">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09922-85811">
09922–85811
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I4RS0B521053.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.975mm" ver = "01" gw = "119" gh = "131"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Press-fit bearing (1) using special tools and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B035">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-76010">
09913–76010
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I7V20A521034.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.568mm" ver = "01" gw = "88" gh = "127"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
